text:
    Printf prints the wrong output in the program below.

How-To-Repeat: 
#include <stdio.h>

main()
{
  printf("%.4e %.4f %.4g\n",0.0,0.0,0.0);
}

prints:
  0e+00 0.0000 0

Should print:

  0.0000e+00 0.0000 0

There are lots of other errors of this kind.  For more examples
build and run the TCL 7.3 tests.
